      <title>俄罗斯占领乌克兰东部要塞塞利多夫中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/russia-captures-center-of-selydove-stronghold-in-ukraine-s-east</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，俄罗斯军队已经占领了波克罗夫斯克之前的最后一座城镇，该城镇是顿涅茨克地区乌克兰军队的重要后勤枢纽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/russia-captures-center-of-selydove-stronghold-in-ukraine-s-east</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 16:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰业银行经济学家称特朗普胜选将带来“毁灭性”政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/scotiabank-economist-derek-holt-says-trump-would-bring-ruinous-economic-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位加拿大顶级经济学家警告说，唐纳德·特朗普的第二任总统任期可能会带来极端的保护主义、巨大的人口负面冲击以及大量债务发行，以资助“完全不受约束的财政政策”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/scotiabank-economist-derek-holt-says-trump-would-bring-ruinous-economic-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非就以色列种族灭绝案提交证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/south-africa-files-evidence-in-israel-genocide-case-at-icj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非周一向国际法院提交了一份卷宗，其中包含所谓的“事实和证据”，以证实以色列在加沙地带犯下种族灭绝罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/south-africa-files-evidence-in-israel-genocide-case-at-icj</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:36:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和特朗普前往摇摆州；马斯克因赠品被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-trump-fan-out-to-swing-states-musk-sued-over-giveaways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普希望在佐治亚州争取福音派选民，而副总统卡马拉·哈里斯则希望在密歇根州巡回演讲中巩固自己在经济方面的地位，距离选举日仅剩八天，两位候选人正在激烈地竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-trump-fan-out-to-swing-states-musk-sued-over-giveaways</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特使称美国制裁使印度银行对俄罗斯贸易持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/us-sanctions-make-indian-banks-wary-of-russia-trade-envoy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫斯科驻新德里特使丹尼斯·阿利波夫表示，印度银行对促进与俄罗斯公司的贸易持谨慎态度，以避免违反美国的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/us-sanctions-make-indian-banks-wary-of-russia-trade-envoy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克因向选举机构提供 100 万美元赠款在宾夕法尼亚州遭起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/elon-musk-sued-over-1-million-election-giveaway-in-philadelphia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克因他所在的政治行动委员会在美国总统大选的最后几天针对摇摆州选民每天举办 100 万美元的抽奖活动而被费城地方检察官起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/elon-musk-sued-over-1-million-election-giveaway-in-philadelphia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗吉尼亚州请求美国最高法院允许清除选民名册</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/virginia-asks-us-supreme-court-to-allow-purge-of-voter-rolls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在遭到下级法院的阻挠后，弗吉尼亚州请求美国最高法院在总统竞选的最后几天恢复该州选民名单清除计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/virginia-asks-us-supreme-court-to-allow-purge-of-voter-rolls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 14:15:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多竞争对手将取消对许多新建住宅征收联邦销售税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 表示，如果他当选总理，他将取消加拿大针对售价低于 100 万加元（719,700 美元）的新房征收的 5% 的全国销售税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友在朝鲜驻军问题上面临有限选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ukraine-allies-face-limited-options-as-north-korea-troops-arrive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯决定派遣朝鲜军队来增强其厌战的军队，这让乌克兰的盟友意识到，如果不进一步升级冲突，他们几乎没有其他应对措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ukraine-allies-face-limited-options-as-north-korea-troops-arrive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉的候选人在圣保罗落败，中间派市长大获全胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/lula-s-pick-loses-in-sao-paulo-capping-local-election-setback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中间派政党是巴西市政选举的最大赢家，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦支持的候选人在圣保罗落败，前总统雅伊尔·博索纳罗支持的另一位候选人在农业强州戈亚斯州首府落败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/lula-s-pick-loses-in-sao-paulo-capping-local-election-setback</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 00:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
